table re2926.combined:
  description: "re.RegexFlag defines __and__/__or__/__xor__ and __rand__/__ror__/__rxor__ (all True) but NOT __iand__/__ior__/__ixor__ — IntFlag's in-place bitwise support is not installed in the subclass __dict__"
